      "content": "I believe it is a problem with the following code:\n```typescript\n        const contributorMinaAU = AccountUpdate.createSigned(contributorAddress);\n        contributorMinaAU.balance.subInPlace(minaAmount);\n        const presaleMinaAU = AccountUpdate.create(this.address);\n        presaleMinaAU.balance.addInPlace(minaAmount);\n```\nIt is a known issue with transferring MINA within the method. The only workaround I know is to move this code from method to Mina.transaction\nSee also https://discord.com/channels/484437221055922177/915745847692636181/1172970400691519498",
