      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "suggest you add the method inside  `TokenizkToken` for approving any AccountUpdate from tokenHolderContract , \n\n``` \n    @method\n    approveAnyAccountUpdate(zkappUpdate: AccountUpdate) {\n        let layout = AccountUpdate.Layout.AnyChildren; \n        let senderAccountUpdate = this.approve(zkappUpdate, layout);\n\n        let negativeAmount = Int64.fromObject(\n            senderAccountUpdate.body.balanceChange\n        );\n        negativeAmount.assertEquals(0); // !!!\n\n        let tokenId = this.token.id;\n        senderAccountUpdate.body.tokenId.assertEquals(tokenId);\n    }\n```\n\nThen, approve the accountUpdate within Mina.transaction block as below:\n``` \n  tx = await Mina.transaction(\n      {\n          sender: feePayer,\n          fee: ctx.txFee,\n          memo: 'user1 contribute',\n      },\n      () => {\n          tokeniZkPresaleZkapp.contribute(presaleParams, redeemAccountZkAppAddress, contributeMinaAmount, whitelistMembershipMerkleWitness, whitelistLeafIndex);\n          basicTokenZkApp.approveAnyAccountUpdate(tokeniZkPresaleZkapp.self);// !!!\n      }\n  );\n\n```",
